WEBVTT

00:08:28.320 --> 00:08:33.056
They all believe that other people
have to stop demonizing.

00:08:33.080 --> 00:08:35.856
They point at politicians,
the media, their neighbor

00:08:35.880 --> 00:08:38.320
or the bus driver
who stops 10 meters away.

00:08:39.600 --> 00:08:42.200
But when I asked, "What about you?

00:08:43.039 --> 00:08:44.280
What can you do?",

00:08:45.360 --> 00:08:47.576
the reply is usually,

00:08:47.600 --> 00:08:49.376
"What can I do?

00:08:49.400 --> 00:08:51.456
I have no influence.

00:08:51.480 --> 00:08:53.160
I have no power."

00:08:54.400 --> 00:08:56.336
I know that feeling.

00:08:56.360 --> 00:08:57.976
For a large part of my life,

00:08:58.000 --> 00:09:03.976
I also thought that I didn't have
any power or influence --